  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00031', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-114-5a5961d5', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '交通事業人員得轉任交通行政機關相當職務。交通行政人員取得交通事業人員任用條例所定各級資位者， 亦得轉任交通事業機構相當職務；其轉任資格、年資提敘等事項之辦法由那個部會定之？', '["由交通部定之", "由銓敘部定之", "由銓敘部會同交通部定之", "由勞動部會同交通部定之"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c174667e9ba2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f5f14ba1000c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "515", "s": "0402", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "交通行政大意", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00032', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-114-5a5961d5', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '為促進國際商港建設及發展，交通部航港局應就入港船舶依其總噸位、離境之上下客船旅客依其人數及 裝卸之貨物依其計費噸量計算，收取商港服務費。商港服務費之費率及收取、保管、運用辦法，係如何 訂定？', '["由交通部航港局訂定後即可施行", "由主管機關訂定後應送行政院備查", "由交通部航港局擬訂，報請主管機關核定", "由交通部航港局擬訂，報請行政院核定"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c174667e9ba2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f5f14ba1000c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "515", "s": "0402", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "交通行政大意", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00033', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-114-5a5961d5', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關公路修建經費負擔原則之敘述何者錯誤？', '["國道、省道由中央負擔", "市道、區道由直轄市政府負擔", "縣道由縣與省轄市政府負擔", "鄉道由鄉鎮與縣轄市政府負擔"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c174667e9ba2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f5f14ba1000c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "515", "s": "0402", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "交通行政大意", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00034', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-114-5a5961d5', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '以詐術或其他不正當方法參加汽車駕駛人、汽車修護技工、汽車檢驗員、汽車駕駛考驗員之考驗或檢定 者，自被查獲日起多少期間內，不得參加該類證照之考驗或檢定？', '["3年", "4年", "5年", "7年"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c174667e9ba2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f5f14ba1000c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "515", "s": "0402", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "交通行政大意", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00035', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-114-5a5961d5', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '汽車運輸業經營不善、妨礙公共利益或交通安全時，經公路主管機關限期改善，逾期不改善或改善而無成 效者，得如何處理？', '["全面接管", "廢止其汽車運輸業執照", "停止其全部營業", "停止其部分營業"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c174667e9ba2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f5f14ba1000c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "515", "s": "0402", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "交通行政大意", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00036', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-114-5a5961d5', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '汽車運輸業之客、貨運運價如何訂定？', '["由公路局擬訂，報請中央公路主管機關核定", "由地方公路主管機關擬訂，報請中央公路主管機關核定", "由汽車運輸業同業公會暨相關之工會按汽車運輸業客、貨運價準則共同擬訂，報請該管公路主管機關核定", "由汽車運輸業同業公會暨相關之工會按汽車運輸業客、貨運價準則共同擬訂後即可施行"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c174667e9ba2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f5f14ba1000c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "515", "s": "0402", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "交通行政大意", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00037', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-114-5a5961d5', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '在核定區域內，以公共汽車運輸旅客為營業者，稱為：', '["市區汽車客運業", "公路汽車客運業", "小客車租賃業", "計程車客運業"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c174667e9ba2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f5f14ba1000c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "515", "s": "0402", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "交通行政大意", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00038', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-114-5a5961d5', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '公路主管機關興建之公路，有下列情形之一者，得向通行之汽車徵收通行費：①為管理交通車流，降低交', '["公路興建係貸款支應者", "公路興建以特種基金支應者", "在同一起訖地點間另闢新線，使 通行車輛受益  ⑤屬於同一交通系統，與既成收費之公路並行  ⑥為挹注公共運輸營運", ""]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c174667e9ba2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f5f14ba1000c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "515", "s": "0402", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "交通行政大意", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00039', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-114-5a5961d5', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '依公路法之規定，有關公路路線劃歸之方式，下列何者錯誤？', '["市區道路與專用公路以外之公路使用同一路線時，其共同使用部分，應劃歸公路路線系統", "區道與市道使用同一路線時，其共同使用部分，應劃歸區道路線系統", "省道與國道使用同一路線時，其共同使用部分，應劃歸國道路線系統", "市道、縣道與省道使用同一路線時，其共同使用部分，應劃歸省道路線系統"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c174667e9ba2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f5f14ba1000c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114010", "c": "515", "s": "0402", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "交通行政大意", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
